{"tid":2430922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］林鄭打BioNTech但鼓勵市民接種科興","createTime":"2021-03-03T09:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T23:37:58.000Z","uid":258340,"like":384,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"26b408caf34d5b147afd036e11bcd3b0c314b699","tid":2430922,"uid":258340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMLiY4m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMLiY4m.png&h=a5124342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭及高官團隊口說接種國產疫苗（科興），為百姓打下強心針，但實情偷偷接種德國疫苗（BioNTech)，更為國家取得更多老人接種國產疫苗（科興）數據，隱瞞科興不能為60以上長者接種的守則，指示那些為名利出賣良心<br />\n摒棄專業操守的醫學專家及權威，推薦愚昧的百姓長者接種疫苗，枉她說自己是香港人的母親，明明就是最毒婦人心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7X9mmv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7X9mmv.png&h=fc0722cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gCB95Ob.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgCB95Ob.png&h=53341ad0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGUS3zS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGUS3zS.png&h=9bb84eb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6836d73f92eff6abdad167d35cf157238e008f8b","tid":2430922,"uid":160662,"like":37,"dislike":7,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:28:53.000Z","msg":"又loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf05fa99fc0afc3b0ec72054be6979ec111a93f","tid":2430922,"uid":214644,"like":42,"dislike":166,"score":-124,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:32:22.000Z","msg":"一早講咗科興有兩種包裝，追下po先啦師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61022d7468140c4cd2dee129198cdc6506272930","tid":2430922,"uid":38633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f